ui5-inspector.name: UI5 Inspector
ui5-inspector.decription: The UI5 Inspector is a standard Chrome extension for debugging and getting to know UI5 applications.

UI5CustomControl.name: OpenUI5 Custom Controls for charting
UI5CustomControl.decription: This project shows how to use C3.js and Chart.js within OpenUI5 projects.

Meteor-UI5.name: Meteor-UI5
Meteor-UI5.decription: Meteor-UI5 is a collection of packages that brings together two powerful open source JavaScript web frameworks: Meteor and OpenUI5.

openui5-i18n-util.name: openui5-i18n-util
openui5-i18n-util.decription: This script will search all your i18n strings and build auto-magically every translations file for you.

Ui5Strap.name: Ui5Strap
Ui5Strap.decription: App Development Toolkit for Desktop, Cloud and Mobile. Based on OpenUI5 + Bootstrap.

XMPPJSONPatchSyncModel.name: XMPPJSONPatchSyncModel
XMPPJSONPatchSyncModel.decription: This OpenUI5 data model uses a node on an XMPP server to synchronize itself to different connected clients.

ui5-model-inspector.name: UI5 Interactive Model Inspector (Custom Control)
ui5-model-inspector.decription: This custom control allows you to view (and modify) state of your client and server models for debugging and development.

ui5-schemas.name: ui5-schemas
ui5-schemas.decription: UI5 Schemas allows you to develop SAPUI5/OpenUI5 XML at a maximum convenience. It downloads, upgrades and sets up SAPUI5/OpenUI5 XML schemas for a better development experience in your favorite IDE (if it is WebStorm ;).

ui5-CRUDModel.name: OpenUI5-SAPUI5-CRUDModel
ui5-CRUDModel.decription: OpenUI5/SAPUI5 Model implementation for mevdschee/php-crud-api and mevdschee/php-api-auth

ui5-jsx-rm.name: JSX to UI5 Babel Plugin
ui5-jsx-rm.decription: A Babel plugin for converting JSX to UI5 render manager calls.
